    title: "AI executes the design. The part that still matters is the part nobody sees.",
    dek: "The most important work in product design has always been upstream of execution: framing the right problem, setting direction, making the judgment call. AI is automating the visible part. What remains is harder to show in a portfolio.",
    author: "Genesis",
