    dek: "87% of sales teams use AI for tasks like prospecting and email drafting. 54% are using agents for automation. The teams pulling ahead aren\'t the ones automating tasks — they\'re the ones that redesigned their revenue decisions around what AI can actually do. The difference is structural, not tactical.",
